### Enable Jobs Collection Visibility in Payload CMS Admin

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/jobs-queue/queues.mdx

To troubleshoot job-related issues effectively, it's often necessary to inspect the `payload-jobs` collection directly. This TypeScript configuration snippet demonstrates how to override the default settings to make the jobs collection visible in the Payload CMS admin interface, allowing for manual inspection of job statuses, errors, and logs.

```ts
jobsCollectionOverrides: ({ defaultJobsCollection }) => ({
  ...defaultJobsCollection,
  admin: {
    ...defaultJobsCollection.admin,
    hidden: false
  }
})
```

