### Adjust Project Structure for Root Admin Panel in PayloadCMS

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/admin/overview.mdx

This example illustrates the necessary project structure modification when the PayloadCMS Admin Panel is configured to run at the root of the application (e.g., `routes.admin` set to '/'). It shows that the dedicated 'admin' directory should be completely removed from the project structure to align with the new routing configuration.

