### Admin Panel Access Control for Collections in Payload CMS using TypeScript

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/access-control/collections.mdx

Configures admin panel access control for a collection by verifying user authentication. This function determines whether a logged-in user can access the admin UI for the specific collection, returning a boolean based on user presence.

```typescript
import type { CollectionConfig } from 'payload'

export const CollectionWithAdminAccess: CollectionConfig = {
  // ...
  access: {
    // highlight-start
    admin: ({ req: { user } }) => {
      return Boolean(user)
    },
    // highlight-end
  },
}
```

