### Implement `adminOnlyFieldAccess` in PayloadCMS (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/ecommerce/plugin.mdx

This `adminOnlyFieldAccess` function provides field-level access control. It checks if the current user possesses the 'admin' role, granting access to the field only if the condition is met.

```typescript
adminOnlyFieldAccess: ({ req: { user } }) =>
  Boolean(user?.roles?.includes('admin'))
```

