### Implement `adminOrPublishedStatus` Access Control in PayloadCMS (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/ecommerce/plugin.mdx

This access control function allows access if the user is an administrator or if the document's status is 'published'. It first checks for admin privileges, then falls back to verifying the document's publication status.

```typescript
adminOrPublishedStatus: ({ req: { user } }) => {
  if (user && Boolean(user?.roles?.includes('admin'))) {
    return true
  }
  return {
    _status: {
      equals: 'published',
    },
  }
}
```
